{"tid":2114474,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"奇洛李維斯撈過界做漫畫編劇","createTime":"2020-07-18T23:11:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T19:26:39.000Z","uid":41343,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"63b3163263a3ab6242f15b08712216307f47b3d1","tid":2114474,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T23:11:24.000Z","msg":"動作片巨星奇洛李維斯（Keanu Reeves）最近撈過界，與著名漫畫出版商Boom! Studio合作，為漫畫《BRZRKR》擔任編劇。奇洛今次會跟著名漫畫創作人Matt Kindt合作編寫劇本，更會與業界名人Alessandro Vitti、Bill Crabtree、Clem Robins和Rafael Grampa合作，該漫畫將於10月出版。<br />\n<br />\n奇洛形容今次跨界合作對他來說，猶如夢想成真：「我自小就愛看漫畫，在藝術上漫畫對我影響頗為深遠！而且今次能與一眾漫畫界傳奇人物合作，對我來說絕對是夢想成真。」<br />\n<br />\n《BRZRKR》是以一名半人半神的傳奇人物Berzerker為主角，擁有不死之身的他經歷千秋萬代之後，最終為美國政府效力，專為他們對付危險敵人。"},{"pid":"dd77f5e7a3995506346304a2d4f4d3cf11f5f5ad","tid":2114474,"uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T23:13:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/geekbase/159502191545.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fgeekbase%2F159502191545.jpg&h=22f5145f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/geekbase/159504917687.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fgeekbase%2F159504917687.jpg&h=21ab7f53&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f58ea1351f9c3d6a3fb0362c5b0e38fd3500acc","tid":2114474,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T23:13:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/geekbase/15950219461.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fgeekbase%2F15950219461.jpg&h=4a34c9cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/geekbase/159504921538.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fgeekbase%2F159504921538.jpg&h=0ec25092&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49f7b0e113ebecb268d604c392e59947110d0e58","tid":2114474,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike"